&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/marketplace/actions/github-pages-action"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>GitHub Pages action&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://gohugo.io/hosting-and-deployment/hosting-on-github/#types-of-github-pages"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>hugo: Host on GitHub&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/marketplace/actions/hugo-setup"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>GitHub Action Hugo setup&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="定制域名">定制域名
&lt;/h3>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>在dns提供商添加cname解析到gh-pages的域名&lt;code>navyd.github.io&lt;/code>。如
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://dns.console.aliyun.com"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>阿里云DNS解析控制台&lt;/a>
&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-27-37.png"
width="710"
height="587"
srcset="/posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-27-37_hu_bd52d07dc6183454.png 480w, /posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-27-37_hu_8885ca076e455353.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="120"
data-flex-basis="290px"
>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>添加域名&lt;code>blog.navyd.xyz&lt;/code>内容到&lt;code>static/CNAME&lt;/code>文件&lt;/li>
&lt;li>根据
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.github.com/en/pages/configuring-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site/managing-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site#configuring-a-subdomain"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Configuring a subdomain&lt;/a>
指导，在github仓库中添加子域名&lt;code>blog.navyd.xyz&lt;/code>并启用https
&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-19-29.png"
width="1433"
height="693"
srcset="/posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-19-29_hu_9359bd7cc0769921.png 480w, /posts/2021/08/my-hugo-blog/2021-08-06-23-19-29_hu_1a692cd09e7e6f91.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="206"
data-flex-basis="496px"
>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>注意：如果用浏览器打开新域名时提示不安全的证书，可能是缓存了以前使用过的域名证书，使用chrome无痕模式可以正常打开，等待chrome刷新缓存即可&lt;/p>
