&lt;h3 id="even主题">even主题
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="主题更改无效">主题更改无效
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>在
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/olOwOlo/hugo-theme-even/blob/master/README-zh.md#theme-color"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Theme Color&lt;/a>
中提到可以在evne目录中&lt;code>/assets/sass/_variable.scss&lt;/code>文件修改主题&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-scss" data-lang="scss">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// ========== Theme Color ========== //
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Config here to change theme color
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Default | Mint Green | Cobalt Blue | Hot Pink | Dark Violet
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span>$theme-color-config&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Dark Violet&amp;#39;&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果未生效可能是由于hugo不是extend版本，使用&lt;code>--tags extended&lt;/code>重新编译&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ hugo version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hugo v0.87.0 linux/amd64 BuildDate&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>unknown
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 在hugo源码内重编译&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ CGO_ENABLED&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span> go install --tags extended
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ hugo version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hugo v0.87.0+extended linux/amd64 BuildDate&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>unknown
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/olOwOlo/hugo-theme-even/issues/350#issuecomment-857537169"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>怎么更该了主题/assets/sass/_variable.scss 颜色值没发生改变是怎么回事&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo#build-and-install-the-binaries-from-source-advanced-install"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Build and Install the Binaries from Source (Advanced Install)&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/olOwOlo/hugo-theme-even/blob/master/README-zh.md#installation"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>even Installation&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h4 id="submodule无法修改">submodule无法修改
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>由于使用了&lt;code>git submodle&lt;/code>将even作为项目的子模块，现在要修改&lt;code>/assets/sass/_variable.scss&lt;/code>文件，但是无法完成。如果之后无法找到解决方法，只有使用clone而不是作为submodule&lt;/p>
